Select Home Warranty

Dependable protection for the home you count on

Help cover the cost of major home system and appliance breakdowns

A single unexpected repair can quickly become expensive. Select Home Warranty offers comprehensive plans designed to help protect your home—and your budget—with less guesswork.

Comprehensive coverage value

Built for real-home wear, tear, and costly surprises

Coverage can include essential home systems and everyday appliances, helping reduce the impact of sudden repair bills and making homeownership feel more predictable.

Helps reduce surprise repair costs

Support when covered items fail from normal use.

Protection for major systems and appliances

A practical safeguard for the parts of the home you rely on most.

Simple quote process

Explore plan options built for homeowners who want budget confidence.

Get Your Free Quote

Select Home Warranty exists to make homeownership feel less vulnerable to the sudden cost of breakdowns. The value of a home warranty plan is not just in the coverage itself, but in the confidence that a malfunctioning system or appliance does not have to disrupt the household budget all at once.

That mission is what gives Select Home Warranty its appeal in a crowded market. The brand reflects a straightforward belief: dependable home protection should be accessible, polished, and practical for everyday homeowners, not reserved for crisis moments alone.

Comprehensive home warranty plans are designed around the reality of normal home use, where major systems and appliances eventually need attention. By focusing on broad protection and a simple quote experience, Select Home Warranty offers a service that feels tailored to the home you depend on every day.

Select Home Warranty  •  Practical protection for the home’s most important essentials

